import React from 'react'
import { Segment, Grid, Container } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function Footer() {
    return (
        <>
            <Segment style={{ position: "static", bottom: 0, padding: "20px", width: "100%" }}
            >
                <Container>
                </Container>
                <Grid divided inverted stackable>
                    <Grid.Row>
                        <Grid.Column width={3}>
                            
                        </Grid.Column>
                    </Grid.Row>


                </Grid>

            </Segment>
        </>
    )
}
